# app/runs/ normally holds local, ephemeral run state and was previously ignored.
# The blanket `runs/` ignore is removed so the committed demo record
# (app/runs/demo-questa-001/) is tracked — it gives the History + Brief viewer
# something to display in the POC demo without needing a live run.
# Note: local run dirs created at runtime are no longer auto-ignored; do not
# `git add` them. Only demo-questa-001/ is intended to be committed.
